videos.headline: SMU strikes first with 16-yard TD
videos.description: Shane Buechele rolls out and connects with Kylen Granson for a SMU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (SMU strikes first with 16-yard TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gainwell takes direct snap 14 yards for Memphis TD
videos.description: Kenneth Gainwell follows blockers and gets into the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Gainwell takes direct snap 14 yards for Memphis TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coxie hauls in one-handed catch
videos.description: Damonte Coxie fights off the SMU cornerback for the 24-yard one-handed catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Coxie hauls in one-handed catch) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones goes up the middle for SMU TD
videos.description: Xavier Jones takes the handoff up the middle for a two-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Jones goes up the middle for SMU TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: White connects with Gibson for 50-yard TD
videos.description: Brady White finds Antonio Gibson wide open down the sideline for a 50-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (White connects with Gibson for 50-yard TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gibson breaks off 97-yard kickoff return for Memphis
videos.description: Antonio Gibson burns SMU for a 97-yard kickoff return touchdown to start the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Gibson breaks off 97-yard kickoff return for Memphis) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: SMU runs reverse flea flicker for 30-yard TD
videos.description: SMU hands it off, reverses it then laterals back to QB Shane Buechele who dimes Kylen Granson for a 30-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (SMU runs reverse flea flicker for 30-yard TD) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Freeman trucks safety on way to 68-yard TD
videos.description: Ke'Mon Freeman powers up the middle for a 68-yard touchdown run for SMU.
